videos.headline: Maryland returner breaks tackle, goes 83 yards for score
videos.description: Maryland's Teldrick Morgan escapes one tackle and jets down the sideline for an 83-yard touchdown return against Rutgers.

videos.headline: Maryland successfully runs a reverse for the touchdown
videos.description: Maryland dual-threat QB Tyrrell Pigrome takes the reverse and runs 28 yards for the score, increasing the Terrapins' lead over Rutgers.

videos.headline: Maryland LB rips ball out of Rutgers RB's hands for turnover
videos.description: Rutgers' Justin Goodwin catches a pass for 30 yards and while running inside the 10-yard line, Maryland's Jermaine Carter Jr. strips the ball from him while taking him to the ground.
